2: Gantt Chart¶

In [4]:
df = pd.DataFrame([
    dict(Task="Tasca 1", Department = 'MKT', Start='2023-04-15', Finish='2023-04-20', Completion = 1.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 2", Department = 'MKT', Start='2023-04-19', Finish='2023-04-24', Completion = 1.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 3", Department = 'IT', Start='2023-04-21', Finish='2023-05-03', Completion = 0.9),
    dict(Task="Tasca 4", Department = 'FIN', Start='2023-04-22', Finish='2023-05-01', Completion = 1.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 5", Department = 'ENG', Start='2023-04-23', Finish='2023-05-09', Completion = 0.5),
    dict(Task="Tasca 6", Department = 'MKT', Start='2023-04-26', Finish='2023-04-27', Completion = 1.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 7", Department = 'FIN', Start='2023-04-27', Finish='2023-05-03', Completion = 0.7),
    dict(Task="Tasca 8", Department = 'MKT', Start='2023-04-28', Finish='2023-05-05', Completion = 0.4),
    dict(Task="Tasca 9", Department = 'FIN', Start='2023-04-28', Finish='2023-05-02', Completion = 1.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 10", Department = 'PROD', Start='2023-05-04', Finish='2023-05-17', Completion = 0.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 11", Department = 'PROD', Start='2023-05-09', Finish='2023-05-13', Completion = 0.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 12", Department = 'ENG', Start='2023-05-10', Finish='2023-05-17', Completion = 0.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 13", Department = 'MKT', Start='2023-05-17', Finish='2023-05-19', Completion = 0.0),
    dict(Task="Tasca 14", Department = 'IT', Start='2023-05-17', Finish='2023-05-20', Completion = 0.0)])

# Dades en format datetime
df['Start'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Start'])
df['Finish'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Finish'])

# Data inici projecte
proj_start = df.Start.min()

# Nmero de dies entre que el projecte comena i l'inici de la tasca
df['start_days'] = (df.Start-proj_start).dt.days

# Nmero de dies desde que comena el projecte i acaba la tasca
df['end_days'] = (df.Finish-proj_start).dt.days

# Dies entre l'inici i final de la tasca
df['days_start_to_end'] = df.end_days - df.start_days

# Dies entre l'inici i la progressi de cada tasca
df['current_days'] = (df.days_start_to_end * df.Completion)

# Colors per departament
def color(row):
    c_dict = {'MKT':'#ff4000', 'FIN':'#ff8000', 'ENG':'#00ff00', 'PROD':'#00bfff', 'IT':'#0000ff'}
    return c_dict[row['Department']]

df['color'] = df.apply(color, axis=1)

##### PLOT #####
fig, (ax, ax1) = plt.subplots(2, figsize=(16,6), gridspec_kw={'height_ratios':[6, 1]})

ax.invert_yaxis()

# Barres
ax.barh(df.Task, df.current_days, left=df.start_days, color=df.color)
ax.barh(df.Task, df.days_start_to_end, left=df.start_days, color=df.color, alpha=0.5)

for idx, row in df.iterrows():
    ax.text(row.end_days+0.1, idx, f"{int(row.Completion*100)}%", va='center', alpha=0.8)
    ax.text(row.start_days-0.1, idx, row.Task, va='center', ha='right', alpha=0.8)

# grid lines
ax.set_axisbelow(True)
ax.xaxis.grid(color='k', linestyle='dashed', alpha=0.4, which='both')

# ticks
xmark = np.arange(0, df.end_days.max()+1, 3)
xmark_labels = pd.date_range(proj_start, end=df.Finish.max()).strftime("%d/%m")
xmark_minor = np.arange(0, df.end_days.max()+1, 1)
ax.set_xticks(xmark)
ax.set_xticks(xmark_minor, minor=True)
ax.set_xticklabels(xmark_labels[::3])
ax.set_yticks([])

# align x axis
ax.set_xlim(0, df.end_days.max())

# remove spines
ax.spines['right'].set_visible(False)
ax.spines['left'].set_visible(False)
ax.spines['left'].set_position(('outward', 10))
ax.spines['top'].set_visible(False)

plt.suptitle('PROJECTE')

##### LEGENDS #####
legend_elements = [Patch(facecolor='#ff4000', label='Marketing'),
                   Patch(facecolor='#ff8000', label='Finance'),
                   Patch(facecolor='#00ff00', label='Engineering'),
                   Patch(facecolor='#00bfff', label='Production'),
                   Patch(facecolor='#0000ff', label='IT')]

legend = ax1.legend(handles=legend_elements, loc='upper center', ncol=5, frameon=False)

# Esborrar eios
ax1.spines['right'].set_visible(False)
ax1.spines['left'].set_visible(False)
ax1.spines['top'].set_visible(False)
ax1.spines['bottom'].set_visible(False)
ax1.set_xticks([])
ax1.set_yticks([])

# Marcar la data d'avui
today = Timestamp('2023-05-02 00:00:00') 
today = today - proj_start

# Dibuixar la lnia today
ax.axvline(today.days, lw=1, alpha=0.7)
ax.text(today.days, len(df)+0.5, 'Today', ha='center')
